    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project car or a source for parts. The exterior has significant paint fading, several large dents, and visible rust spots on the lower panels. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention for a persistent oil leak and a rough idle, while the transmission shifts harshly. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional air conditioning system. It is recommended that any potential buyer brings a mechanic for a thorough inspection before purchase.",
